Revision history for Perl extension Smart-Args-TypeTiny

0.10 2017-10-26T04:33:54Z

    - isa/does can take type constraint string
    - support Mouse::Util::TypeConstraints for Smart::Args compatible
    - args/args_pos return hashref of parameters
    - optional parameter allows to pass undef
    - coderef of default parameter returns as scalar context

